## MapViewImageCache.clear() method

Remove all \[\[ImageItem\]\]s from the cache. Also removes all \[\[ImageItem\]\]s that belong to this \[\[MapView\]\] from the global \[\[ImageCache\]\].

```typescript
clear(): void;
```
